{
  "doc_id": "19651",
  "text": "As a specific realisation based on this approach, we have integrated a recently introduced machine learning-based semantic class disambiguation system capable of offering multiple outputs with probability estimates that was shown to be able to reduce ambiguity on average by over 75% while retaining the correct class in on average 99% of cases over six corpora [CITATION_1] . Section 4 presents an evaluation of the contribution of this component to annotator productivity.",
